songs.name: Blackbird
songs.lyrics: Blackbird singing in the dead of night. Take these broken wings and learn to fly

songs.name: Walk The Line
songs.lyrics: I keep a close watch on this heart of mine. I keep my eyes wide open all the time

songs.name: All Over Again
songs.lyrics: We're falling all over again, like a flash back to way back when.. Back when we were us.

songs.name: Out Of The Woods
songs.lyrics: Looking at it now, it all seems so simple. We were laying on your couch, I remember.

songs.name: Delicate
songs.lyrics: We might lay like never before. When there's nothing to give, how can we ask for more.

songs.name: Silver Dagger
songs.lyrics: Go court another tender maiden and hope that she will be your wife. For I have been warned and I've decided to sleep alone all of my life.
